ice\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The case is made from Venezia leather and features a unique patina with Olympic rings inspired colour mix.\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1134, \"end\": 1141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venice\", \"score\": 0.995353830785643, \"rank\": 0.004667856834021477, \"text\": \"Venezia\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venice\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venice\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The case\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique patina\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1178}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic rings\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1197}, {\"ngram\": \"colour mix\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Samsung handed over the special foldable phone to every Paris 2024 athlete even before the device went on sale around the globe.\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"score\": 0.9997779515797438, \"rank\": 0.0002220808656507494, \"text\": \"Samsung\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung\"}, {\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999965714798348, \"rank\": 3.4285320089532635e-06, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the special foldable phone\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"the device\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"sale\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1330}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Offered to every competing athlete, thecomes loaded with 100GB of data and unlimited texts and calls, allowing athletes to get online and stay connected with friends and family throughout the event.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every competing athlete\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"100GB\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"unlimited texts\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"calls\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also comes with a range offeatures such as live translation of calls and a text compose that will allow athletes to reach out to more audience clearly.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a range offeatures\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1586}, {\"ngram\": \"live translation\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"calls\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"a text compose\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"more audience\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to this, the foldable device also gets an AI-backed interpreter that can instantly translate live conversations, allowing athletes to chat with other athletes and volunteers and receive a live translation of what they are saying on screen, while still speaking face-to-face.\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"the foldable device\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"an AI-backed interpreter\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"live conversations\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1846}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"volunteers\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"a live translation\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"screen\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"face\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 1989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although the Samsung Galaxy Z Flip 6 Olympic Edition may be quite tempting for technology enthusiasts and collectors, it is not available for the general public and is only offered to around 17,000 athletes participating in the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2005, \"end\": 2021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_series\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Samsung Galaxy Z\", \"types\": [\"Q1067263\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_series\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samsung_Galaxy_Z_series\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"technology enthusiasts\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"collectors\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"the general public\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"around 17,000 athletes\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Written by: Ayushmann Chawla,\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}]}"